{"title":"笑贪官","authors":["吴震启"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":9,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑贪官"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴震启"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说那贪官，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑那贪官，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看他面带微笑楚楚衣冠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸皮磨厚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脑袋削尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管那儿有缝没缝都往里钻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欲壑难填心术险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"权名利色都占全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白日里门庭若市，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半夜里心惊胆战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活落个身败名裂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死难逃遗臭万年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间一到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满盘清算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有道是杀人的偿命欠债的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还钱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"法网恢恢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疏而不漏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑贪官你欺人欺世又怎能"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欺天！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}